  "description": "Ingest a transcript PDF dropped in OneDrive, use the Anthropic Claude piece to extract the issuing country and the grades, resolve the matching scale via POST /scales/match (ranked by grade coverage), then run the transfer for the covered grades. A Router uploads a needs-review JSON instead when no scale can be confidently resolved. Backend calls are done with the HTTP piece (Pieces variant).",
